lead_paragraph: Ian Johnson ran for 147 yards and 3 touchdowns and Jared Zabransky passed for 299 yards to lead No. 12 Boise State to a 38-7 victory against Nevada yesterday, all but clinching a spot in the Bowl Championship Series for the Broncos.
